1. 환경 설정 <br>
https://confluence.kaonmedia.com/pages/viewpage.action?pageId=71994414
@code
- QE 에 xTS 툴이 들어 있는 USB 를 받아 최신버전으로 변경
- STB 기본 설정
	Factory reset
	Languge : English (United States)
	Location : On
	Connect to Wi-Fi 
	Developer option : On
	Google settings → Device Preferences → About → Build 7회 선택 → Google settings → Developer option
		✔ Stay awake : On
		✔ USB debugging : On
		✔ Verify apps over USB : Off
- 공장초기화 수행
- wifi 테스트시 usb 무선랜을 USB로 연결하고 LAN포트 이용하여 ADB연결 
  히든메뉴>제조사메뉴>네트워크설정>1way
  Google settings -> Network & Internet : wifi off / Scanning alwasy available off
@endcode

2. cts - user 펌웨어<br>
https://confluence.kaonmedia.com/display/GQE/xTS%29+CTS
@code
$ adb devices
$ adb connect 192.168.0.10:5555
$ cd android-cts/tools/ 
$ ./cts-tradefed  
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsJniTestCases -t android.jni.cts.JniStaticTest#test_dlopenPublicLibraries
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsWifiTestCases -t android.net.wifi.cts.WifiManagerTest#testNetworkSetupWizardPermission
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsWifiTestCases -t android.net.wifi.cts.WifiManagerTest#testNetworkStackPermission
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsIntentSignatureTestCases -t android.signature.cts.intent.IntentTest#shouldNotFindUnexpectedIntents
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsAppSecurityHostTestCases -t android.appsecurity.cts.ExternalStorageHostTest#testExternalStorageWrite
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsAppSecurityHostTestCases -t android.appsecurity.cts.ExternalStorageHostTest#testExternalStorageRead29
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsAppSecurityHostTestCases -t android.appsecurity.cts.StorageHostTest#testVerifyStatsMultiple
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsAppSecurityHostTestCases -t android.appsecurity.cts.StorageHostTest#testVerifyStatsExternal
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsAppSecurityHostTestCases -t android.appsecurity.cts.StorageHostTest#testVerifyStatsExternalConsistent
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsAppSecurityHostTestCases -t android.appsecurity.cts.StorageHostTest#testVerifyStats
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsAppSecurityHostTestCases -t android.appsecurity.cts.ListeningPortsTest#testNoRemotelyAccessibleListeningTcp6Ports
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsInputMethodTestCases -t android.view.inputmethod.cts.KeyboardVisibilityControlTest#testImeState_Unspecified_EditorDialogLostFocusAfterUnlocked
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsInputMethodTestCases -t android.view.inputmethod.cts.KeyboardVisibilityControlTest#testImeState_Visible_EditorDialogLostFocusAfterUnlocked
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsInputMethodTestCases -t android.view.inputmethod.cts.KeyboardVisibilityControlTest#testImeState_AlwaysVisible_EditorDialogLostFocusAfterUnlocked
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsInputMethodTestCases -t android.view.inputmethod.cts.KeyboardVisibilityControlTest#testImeState_AlwaysHidden_EditorDialogLostFocusAfterUnlocked
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsInputMethodTestCases -t android.view.inputmethod.cts.KeyboardVisibilityControlTest#testImeState_Hidden_EditorDialogLostFocusAfterUnlocked
cts-tf > run cts -m CtsPermissionTestCases -t android.permission.cts.OneTimePermissionTest#testPermissionRevokedOnKill
